import React from 'react'
//import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import SidebarMenu from 'react-bootstrap-sidebar-menu';
import '~react-bootstrap-sidebar-menu/dist/sidebar-menu.scss'

const Navbar = () => {
   return (
    <Sidebar>
  <Sidebar.Collapse>
    <Sidebar.Header>
      <Sidebar.Brand>1</Sidebar.Brand>
      <Sidebar.Toggle />
    </Sidebar.Header>

    <Sidebar.Body>
      <Sidebar.Nav>

        <Sidebar.Nav.Link>
          <Sidebar.Nav.Icon>2</Sidebar.Nav.Icon>
          <Sidebar.Nav.Title>Home</Sidebar.Nav.Title>
        </Sidebar.Nav.Link>

        <Sidebar.Sub>
          <Sidebar.Sub.Toggle>
            <Sidebar.Nav.Icon />
            <Sidebar.Nav.Title>About</Sidebar.Nav.Title>
          </Sidebar.Sub.Toggle>
          <Sidebar.Sub.Collapse>
            <Sidebar.Nav>

              <Sidebar.Nav.Link>
                <Sidebar.Nav.Icon>3</Sidebar.Nav.Icon>
                <Sidebar.Nav.Title>Contact</Sidebar.Nav.Title>
              </Sidebar.Nav.Link>

            </Sidebar.Nav>
          </Sidebar.Sub.Collapse>
        </Sidebar.Sub>

      </Sidebar.Nav>
    </Sidebar.Body>

  </Sidebar.Collapse>
</Sidebar>

   )
}

export default Navbar;
